constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Erection of 4 interlinked residential buildings of between 4 to 8-storeys in height to provide 215 flats, comprising 66 x one bed and 149 x 2 bedroom flats together with 175 parking spaces, new vehicular access, pedestrian footpath and link staircase to A12, riverside walkway, associated hard and soft landscaping and public art feature.
